Package: reco
Type: Package
Title: Matrix factorizations for recommender systems
Version: 0.2.0
Author: Dmitriy Selivanov
Maintainer: Dmitriy Selivanov <selivanov.dmitriy@gmail.com>
Description: Matrix factorizations for recommender systems. 
    Following algorithms are implemented at the moment: 
    1) ALS for implicit feedback (Cholesky solver, Conjugate Gradient solver)
    2) ALS for explicit feedback
    All algorithms work on sparse matrices and reasonably fast and parallelized if possible.
